      • deleteBatchActions

        public static AylaAPIRequest deleteBatchActions(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> batchActionUUIDSet,
                                                com.android.volley.Response.Listener<java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String>> successListener,
                                                ErrorListener errorListener)
        Delete BatchActions from the Datum given a set of BatchAction UUID's.This lists only deleted the list of BatchActions whose UUID's match the ones passes in parameter batchActionUUIDSet.We make sure that these actions already exist in user Datum and deleted only those BatchActions.This method returns the List of Batch UUID's that were successfully deleted.
        参数:
        batchActionUUIDSet - ArrayList of BatchActions
        successListener - Listener to receive on successful deletion and contains the actions that were deleted
        errorListener - Listener to receive an AylaError should one occur
        返回:
        the AylaAPIRequest object
